<i>adverb</i>: 요행히 [요행히], 다행히 [다행히], 다행스레 [다행스레] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>요행히 [요행히]</dt><br>
<dd>fortunately; luckily</dd><br>
<dd>뜻밖으로 운수가 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>With good luck by chance.</dd><br>
<dt>다행히 [다행히]</dt><br>
<dd>luckily; with luck</dd><br>
<dd>뜻밖에 운이 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>Luckily unexpected.</dd><br>
<dt>다행스레 [다행스레]</dt><br>
<dd>luckily; with luck</dd><br>
<dd>예상보다 상황이 나쁘지 않아서 운이 좋은 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Seemingly lucky because the situation is not as bad as expected.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>